snippet: Hawaiian Airlines and Delta Air Lines again topped the airline on-time rankings for November, released on Friday by the Transportation Department.
abstract: Transportation Department reports Hawaiian Airlines and Delta Air Lines ranked highest for on-time flights in November, while budget airlines Spirit and Frontier had worst on-time performance and highest number of complaints.
lead_paragraph: Hawaiian Airlines and Delta Air Lines again topped the airline on-time rankings for November, released on Friday by the Transportation Department.

headline.main: Hawaiian Airlines and Delta Lead On-Time Rankings
